            <h2>Radiate Cathcart</h2>
            <span class="section-heading-rule" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </div>

        <div class="card-content-with-image">
            <div>
                <p>Radiate Cathcart is a joint youth ministry supported by all three
                Cathcart churches. Drawing inspiration from Philippians 2:15 — to
                "shine like stars" — Radiate engages young people through worship,
                fellowship, discipleship and community service.</p>

                <p>Led by Senior Development Worker Cara Wightman, Radiate's programme
                includes weekly and monthly groups, Easter and summer holiday clubs,
                and The Vibe creative arts project, supported by the Church of Scotland
                Go For It Fund.</p>

